<h1>Trophy Tracker</h1>
<div class="homepageDescription">
    <p>
        Trophy Tracker is a cross-platform video game achievement tracking system that consolidates trophy and
        achievement data across multiple gaming platforms (including Steam, PlayStation, Xbox, and Nintendo Switch)
        into one centralized location. Players who game across several platforms can finally see all of their
        unlocked achievements in one place.
    </p>
    <p>
        Use the navigation links above to manage the following:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong class="pageLabel">Players</strong> - Manage player accounts.</li>
        <li><strong class="pageLabel">Games</strong> - Manage the game library.</li>
        <li><strong class="pageLabel">Platforms</strong> - Manage gaming platforms.</li>
        <li><strong class="pageLabel">Achievements</strong> - Manage achievements associated with games and platforms.</li>
        <li><strong class="pageLabel">Players Games</strong> - Track which games each player owns.</li>
        <li><strong class="pageLabel">Players Achievements</strong> - Track which achievements each player has earned.</li>
        <li><strong class="pageLabel">Game Platforms</strong> - Track which platforms each game is available on.</li>
    </ul>
</div>
